## Test Data

The bundled CSV (`script/influx_testdata_augmented.csv`) contains:

| Property | Value |
|---|---|
| `_measurement` | `m` |
| `_field` | `mem` |
| Tags | `host` (A/B/C), `region` (east), `env` (prod/staging/dev), `service` (billing/api/ml), `rack` (r1/r2/r3), `az` (a/b) |
| Time range | `2025-08-31 00:52` – `2025-08-31 04:52` |

To test with more diverse data, upload additional CSVs with different measurements and fields to InfluxDB via the UI (Load Data → CSV).
